Part 2.3-a

# i.) name is not usefull for the model because there is no correlation between name and mpg so we can cut it out right away
set.seed(1122)
index <- sample(1:nrow(Auto),0.95*dim(Auto)[1])
train.df <- Auto[index,]
test.df <- Auto[-index,]
autoT_model <- lm(mpg ~ . - name, data = train.df )
summary(autoT_model)
